===Alternative forms===
* {{l|ast|xuzgar}}
===Etymology===
From {{inh|ast|la|jūdicāre}}, {{m|la|iūdicāre}}, present active infinitive of {{m|la|iūdicō||pass judgement}}. Compare {{cog|es|juzgar}}, {{cog|gl|xulgar}}, {{cog|pt|julgar}}.
